{"tid":561193,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"如果美股喺港股休市呢幾日冧檔會點","createTime":"2018-02-14T21:08:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-15T07:50:46.000Z","uid":90595,"like":15,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"692827bec538c1911661c93c8f72ab5de2045c52","tid":561193,"uid":90595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T21:08:00.000Z","msg":"留意番<br />\n- 10年債息今晚企穩左2.9<br />\n- 美日匯率跌穿108 就快企穩107<br />\n- 金價喺呢6hr由1330彈到1355<br />\n- 呢兩日美股同恆指成交量低<br />\n- 美股由26500落23400, 而家反彈到24900, 換句話說已經彈番一半<br />\n<br />\n如果美股喺港股休市呢幾日冧檔會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"> <br />\n另外唔關事嘅係美帝人民恭賀全球人情人節快樂 另祝中國人民新春快樂</span>"},{"pid":"75b6569031c8fe0001d5b35c54e06050003be503","tid":561193,"uid":90595,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T21:17:43.000Z","msg":"btw 唔啱聽嘅咪插我 陳列事實 好友淡友心裡有數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e243b41d36269b65c93b6254d3b333a0bb7f664","tid":561193,"uid":62424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T21:19:26.000Z","msg":"所以話千萬唔好持貨過新年"},{"pid":"8be5dd8b4e496ee63d670d74b2de989d5daca545","tid":561193,"uid":38049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75b6569031c8fe0001d5b35c54e06050003be503","tid":561193,"uid":90595,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T21:17:43.000Z","msg":"btw 唔啱聽嘅咪插我 陳列事實 好友淡友心裡有數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T21:25:20.000Z","msg":"咁點解 個 VIX 會跌咁多嘅"},{"pid":"1670e616186aabff02a37b154851c820c4f3edf7","tid":561193,"uid":90595,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"8be5dd8b4e496ee63d670d74b2de989d5daca545","tid":561193,"uid":38049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75b6569031c8fe0001d5b35c54e06050003be503","tid":561193,"uid":90595,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T21:17:43.000Z","msg":"btw 唔啱聽嘅咪插我 陳列事實 好友淡友心裡有數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T21:25:20.000Z","msg":"咁點解 個 VIX 會跌咁多嘅"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T21:42:11.000Z","msg":"VIX唔係strictly leading indicator <br />\n佢透過量度認購同認沽期權嘅價格變化，你個市大跌觸發左嗰刻之後， 期權價格先會變動。<br />\n呢個星期個市平穩番，期權價格冇大變動，VIX就自然會低番。<br />\n你compare DJI 同 VIX兩張圖就見到，<br />\n例如VIX升超過20時係香港時間2月6日0200, 而呢個時間DJI 已經(由26300)跌到落25100, 所以<br />\n另外而家VIX 19 20左右，以前係極少高過13 ，我理解20呢個 level為「都唔低，隨時都有機會大跌」，但其實VIX只能較為準確地睇「當大跌開始或已經被觸發後，以options反映嘅投資情緒喺30日内仲有幾震盪」。"},{"pid":"d881b91efc1f4afa9187eb39f04c19d10a9962dc","tid":561193,"uid":90595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T21:47:38.000Z","msg":"例如VIX升超過20時係香港時間2月6日0200, 而呢個時間DJI 已經(由26300)跌到落25100, 所以<span style=\"color: red;\">當市場情緒較冷淡時去用VIX來預測將來突如其來嘅大幅波動並唔準確</span>"},{"pid":"b761c0ac5387754c6ca4a30f2372dcf7ee661ae3","tid":561193,"uid":43215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T21:58:35.000Z","msg":"我覺得老美果邊對息口e樣野超恐慌，<br />\n岩岩出CPI果時即轉跌，所以個恐慌情緒仲係度。如果E幾日有突發事會再調整<br />\n<br />\n利申 9UP，覺得係牛市但未調整完"},{"pid":"49679cd5ba6dfec195e87697d237d2bcdf73ab88","tid":561193,"uid":91648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T22:37:32.000Z","msg":"債息升嘅消息已經消化。<br />\n金價升純粹係反映美匯指數。CPI 略低於市場預測，加息壓力稍減，美匯跌。"},{"pid":"5c2bfe58c2de20aaef2fec8dd46f26494b357d32","tid":561193,"uid":155710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T00:33:46.000Z","msg":"星期一老美President day唔開市都係得星期五一日"},{"pid":"6fb0ff8398f984aa98cbbe6a4fce8892ebe18156","tid":561193,"uid":56688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T00:38:31.000Z","msg":"閉門打狗"},{"pid":"15ab4a6c831297fdcd9e1e5649ea1748688cf004","tid":561193,"uid":102179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T00:41:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f230d7456d0f37